This paper deals with the capacity analysis of a MIMO two-way relay channel, which involves information theory, networking, and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SI (Signal Processing), cs.COMM (Communication), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
